description: This file provides platform-dependent and utility functions for Web Resource Owner objects, including the creation of resource owner instances, with an implementation of the WebCreateResourceOwner function that calls WebRooCreate.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE WebCreateResourceOwner(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates a new Web Resource Owner object by delegating to WebRooCreate, passing through context handles.
